{"tid":1497761,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"今晚人鏈要人！今晚人鏈要人！","createTime":"2019-08-23T06:15:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-23T08:00:02.000Z","uid":308414,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"fda0b7ad9cc82cf8c894d1a82f159063f94b5a60","tid":1497761,"uid":308414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T06:15:52.000Z","msg":"係呀 條人鏈係好膠㗎<br />\nOn99企定定喺度拖手唔知做咩<br />\n但係我哋今晚都係要去做 而且人數一定要夠多<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">點解？</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">第一 可以藉住呢件事connect波羅的海三國乃至成個西方世界</span><br />\n當年佢哋就係憑着呢件事展示比世界知佢哋脫離蘇聯嘅決心 <br />\n今日我哋面對住嘅都係共產極權國家<br />\n模仿當年佢哋嘅行為係非常之有標誌性 <br />\n同時都能喚起西方世界冷戰時候嘅回憶 <br />\n呼喚佢哋加入對抗中國嘅陣營<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">第二 場面好有震撼性 可以吸引外國媒體報道 </span><br />\n我知有啲人覺得咁樣做真心膠 <br />\n仲廢過遊行集會<br />\n但係外國媒體最鍾意影呢啲多人做嘅膠嘢<br />\n可能你會話對外國嘅文宣已經做得好多<br />\n但係仲未夠呀 香港要贏除咗靠自己抗爭之外<br />\n最重要係來自外國嘅支持！<br />\n無論我哋喺Twitter po幾多張文宣圖都好 <br />\n一張來自外國記者影嘅相造成嘅影響一定更加大<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">點都好  只要方法係有可能有效嘅我哋都應該去試</span><br />\n<br />\n所以<br />\n唔該大家今晚真係出嚟幫下手組成呢條人鏈<br />\n依家睇返<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">報咗到話去嘅人數係完全唔夠！！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n無論你原本喺呢場運動入邊嘅角色係咩都好<br />\n攰嘅喺屋企休息一下 <br />\n時間允許嘅話就落屋企樓下個地鐵站幫下手<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">多你一個真係差好多！！！</span>"},{"pid":"4f946af7ab4d14f0a49e1f7062512d99b9b6eae2","tid":1497761,"uid":308414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T06:16:38.000Z","msg":"P牌仔推唔郁 有冇好心人入嚟幫下手<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"926fba14083d4a19079f9984ec993b0c19f2dd2f","tid":1497761,"uid":166273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T06:17:06.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">612 721 811<br />\n<br />\n823 人鏈<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;823 23:59死線&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1494948\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1494948</a><br />\n<br />\n824 朝早7點機場<br />\n<br />\n824 晏晝1點觀塘<br />\n<br />\n825 荃葵青<br />\n <br />\n831 中聯辦<br />\n<br />\n9月頭三罷同塞爆機場<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">不分和勇！永不割席！<br />\n<br />\n香港人 請為自由而戰<br />\nFight for freedom, Stand with Hong Kong</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>光復香港 時代革命</strong></span><br />\nLiberate Hong Kong, Revolution of our times</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div>"},{"pid":"b581cfe141632fc6c097b773f2be2c9347076a5e","tid":1497761,"uid":133743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T06:17:53.000Z","msg":"大家唔使怕醜，一齊出黎"},{"pid":"5b08254362ec3ce11ddc67c64f139b4623818d4d","tid":1497761,"uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T06:18:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\"